{{Infobox dungeon |name = Victory Road Johto |image = [[File:Victory Road Johto.png|thumb]] |caption = A map of Victory Road Johto. |tokens = 7,000 |location = Route 26, south of Indigo Plateau Johto. }} '''Victory Road Johto''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Johto]]. It initially has 36 tiles arranged in a 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 15 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 128,500 HP.
